Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You've been real quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl with the sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is that kid one of the Five Swords, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaba Tsukuyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Academy's strongest pigtailed girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The only middle-school student in the Five Swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a cool beauty that guys, girls,\Nand even the Five Swords are terrified of!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get my last stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's super dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.63,0:00:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even see her draw her sword,\Nor put it back in her damn scabbard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You died just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:10.46,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,900)\blur1.5\pos(750.3,889.2)\}Episode 9
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:10.46,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,900)\blur1.5\pos(1380.9,889.2)\fscx80}The Terrifying Blade, Inaba Tsukuyo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You died just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I didn't cut you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will only stop my blade for you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you need an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Truthfully, the school headmaster has\Nentrusted me with your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me to allow you two transgressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you have surpassed that limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your first transgression was breaking into\NOnigawara's room in the girls' dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise, your second was breaking into\NTamaba's room and the bathing area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignoring my summons was your third transgression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, I have a slight cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the nature of this academy,\NI am not driven to anger by small things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the girls' dorm is another matter altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My attendant manages the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Attendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All responsibility falls on her shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The patience of the Buddha has its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have reached mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,T-time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-why is a kid like you in charge of me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are plenty of reasons, but there are two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...big reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One, I am stronger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:04:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you doing all this needless killing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls your age should love butterflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Moths, I could get...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The flapping sound they make irritates me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally, I can't tell the difference\Nbetween moths and butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Blind, what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have good hearing to make up for it,\Nso do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I'd like to continue my explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you realized it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I performed the technique just now at kotsu,\Nor one hundredth speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just barely saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord4.5\blur4.5\pos(871.999,555)\3c&HDCD9E0&}Kotsu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Yakumaru Jigen School sword draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all, the speed of your first attack, too fast\Nto be seen by the human eye, has its own name:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Invisible Blade, Unyou,\None hundred-thousandth speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.25,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\bord4.5\pos(958.001,573)}Unyou
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A fellow student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura, you can use a sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Could use is more accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing an attack at kotsu speed\Nis an extremely rare ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps your talents were honed to\Nthat level by intensive training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I am extremely disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You swordsman capabilities are already falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You were not blessed with a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you were still able to tell I was a fellow student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For one, you reside on a different level of speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides destructive force and reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,one big difference between fists and kicks\Nand the sword is speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The point of each weapon accelerates\Nin proportion to its length.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If, even with your bare hands,\Nyou can face someone with a sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that means you must have previously lived\Nin that environment yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,From that, I can logically conclude\Nyou also have experience with the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent deduction, Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Finished already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good, it's deeper than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to scuff my boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\pos(958.001,660.999)}Pickaxe Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.90,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\pos(958.001,660.999)}Tiger's Claw
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\pos(958.001,660.999)}Spread Fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:48.90,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\pos(958.001,660.999)}Four-Speared Hands
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyo-bo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt as to why Jigen techniques came to\Nhave a large advantage over bare-handed combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, there was a great karate master\Nwho had full mastership of Jigen School.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\bord4.5\pos(946.001,733)}Auto-Counter: Gouging Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at the good part. Don't get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You! I told you not to follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, come at me together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And, above all, your technique\Nwhen employing your magic bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The collision on the median line of your\Niliopsoas muscles deep within your core.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a secret technique only given\Nto a small fraction of students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That is how I determined you were\Na fellow student of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that, you heard it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some kinda commotion going on on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the Empress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the name of your magic bullet\Nfrom the Empress as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you two are acquainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From the first day she transferred here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the aloof Empress didn't try to get along with anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but she spoke of you fondly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you have not spent time with her\Nsince coming here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but are the two of you friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Onigawara, Kikakujo, Hanasaka, and Tamaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In the blink of an eye, you've made friends\Nwith the other four Swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you are quite good at making friends,\Nbut how did things come to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey, Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very different from the "Amou" you speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew about my magic bullet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That means she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please spare them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me and only me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot let...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Warabi Hanasaka, you are an arrogant soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrificing yourself will save no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cannot bear to watch, then shut your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,before I do something even more horrific before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What were those voices just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Screams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard my voice raised before like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My ears hurt from hearing my own voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The... Empress...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Amou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaka! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about me, the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not hurt as bad as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, some--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem upset, Inaba Tsukuyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, when my anger surpasses\Na certain level, I smile instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You too should carouse in moderation, Empress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hide anything from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you alright with just watching them die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't really my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be best if you averted your eyes\Nfrom what's going to happen next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Amou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Those screams earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain to me exactly what those were!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you get away with\Ndoing whatever that was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no need to rush,\NI'll recreate the scene for you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...with your bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She was behind me all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear her or even feel her presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will examine her wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Her eyes are alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but the injury to her eyelids\Nis down to the orbital fascia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't open her eyes on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll need surgery, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can help with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Those girls...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(460,768.499)\bord4.5\blur4.5}Balestra
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1465.999,761)\bord4.5\blur4.5}Mist
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:54.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(948,627)\b1\bord4.5\blur4.5}Roundhouse Block
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Amou's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Defense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:16:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no reason to be fighting you morons seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You uncivilized girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.69,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(954,655)\i0\b1\bord4.5\blur4.5}Foot Blade: Two-Sided Kick
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, you could never work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but now, you're attacking me in tandem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he bring about this change?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it didn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even her feet are blades...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like the Nemean lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My bladed hands are a product of hardening my body,\Nyet you thought it was a special talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But that fact isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The fundamental skill is turning your body\Ninto a single blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ultimate form of karate,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Takemikazuchi, the Sword God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.24,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\fscx80\pos(995.999,633)}Takemikazuchi, Sword from Body
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Her whole body is a weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong when I thought you were\Nusing a style of swordsmanship...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Swordsman Without a Sword,\NAmou Kirukiru's true form
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,was a karate practitioner who turned\Nher own hands and feet into blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Non!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Depeche-toi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but if we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You Onee-samaes will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaba Tsukuyo, you intend to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one question for you, Mozunono.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nono...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, u-uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes, we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:18:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As you've just heard, we are friends, and I will not\Nexcuse anyone who lays a hand on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's because I met with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,for I'm so bold today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's earlier than I'd planned, but really,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,my ultimate karate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,against your sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find out which is superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okinawan Kobudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A style of karate from Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no first strike in karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the pace of bare-handed combat\Ncannot keep up with the speed of a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why you have your auto-counters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In Uechi School, one of the three great schools of\NOkinawan karate, the body is literally beaten into steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Similarly, reacting to blows\Nwith a spear hand is done in sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The cerebellum memorizes behavior patterns,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but these patterns can be burned in deeper\Nwhen physical damage is incorporated into that training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Through repetition of these excessive sessions,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,these patterns were ingrained even to\Nthe level of spinal cord reflex arcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, your Takemikazuchi is\Ngo no sen, after the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My Unyou is sen no sen, faster than the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The names of both these techniques\Ninvoke lightning, but on opposite poles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning your body into a blade\Nand tempering it thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no easy feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You could simply carry it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you still think you can beat me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be very disappointed in your underestimating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost summer,\Nbut I feel the temperature just dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If Satori is a monster, then the two of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are a devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a behemoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\pos(1012.001,699)}One Second, Three Strikes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,667)\bord4.5\blur4.5}Unyou: Flash of Light
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nono!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Too fast to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She broke through Amou's Takemikazuchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.34,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\bord4.5\pos(906,697)}Auto-Counter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She took damage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A tie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If it had been a real sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a sharpened blade, I don't know how things\Nwould have turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's light and so horribly weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A safe, cheap, fake metal sword,\Nmade from a zinc alloy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A child's toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Swordsmen have it so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't fight without a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get my wits about me today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be his fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Amou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Omugi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiko here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The last of the Five Swords is Inaba Tsukuyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the strongest, fiercest pigtailed girl on the planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She uses Yakumaru Jigen School!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She draws her blade at unyou speed,\Nundetectable by the naked eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so fast, you can't even see it! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.50,0:23:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll watch out for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.04,0:23:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stop it with the bad puns?!
